g></a>D. 折叠icon<code class=\"language-text\">可选</code></h5>\n<ul>\n<li>示意用户此处为折叠内容，可进行操作</li>\n<li>通常位于面板右侧或标题文案左侧</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">种类</th>\n<th align=\"center\">面板背景(A)</th>\n<th align=\"center\">标题(B)</th>\n<th align=\"center\">内容区(C)</th>\n<th align=\"center\">折叠icon（D）</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">常规</td>\n<td align=\"center\">可选</td>\n<td align=\"center\">✓</td>\n<td align=\"center\">✓</td>\n<td align=\"center\">可选</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">手风琴</td>\n<td align=\"center\">可选</td>\n<td align=\"center\">✓</td>\n<td align=\"center\">✓</td>\n<td align=\"center\">可选</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"基本样式\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"基本样式 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>基本样式</h2>\n<h3 id=\"类型\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\" aria-label=\"类型 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>类型</h3>\n<p>根据内容展示逻辑不同，分为