eft\">默认</td>\n<td align=\"left\">默认初始状态，折叠面板为收起状态</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">悬停</td>\n<td align=\"left\">鼠标经过面板可进行点击操作时，切换至悬停状态，鼠标变为点击样式<!--（这个状态图上🈚️）--></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">选中</td>\n<td align=\"left\">点击选中折叠面板后，面板展开展示对应详细内容</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">禁用</td>\n<td align=\"left\">当面板不可展开时，状态为禁用不可点击状态</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">加载中</td>\n<td align=\"left\">异步操作</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"设计说明\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E\" aria-label=\"设计说明 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>设计说明</h2>\n<h3 id=\"原则\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99\" aria-label=\"原则 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>原则</h3>\n<p>在界面中如何使用该组件？</p>\n<h4 id=\"1效率\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87\" aria-label=\"1效率 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.效率</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>简化流程</strong>：将信息进行结构化的展示和隐藏，操作流程简洁直观，表达清晰，让用户快速理解并进行操作</li>\n<li><strong>帮助用户识别</strong>：符合用户操作习惯，通过直白设计，帮助用户快速识别，减少学习负担和试错成本</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"2反馈\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2%E5%8F%8D%E9%A6%88\" aria-label=\"2反馈 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.反馈</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>控制反馈</strong>：通过界面样式和交互动效让用户清晰感知操作</li>\n<li><strong>页面反馈</strong>：用户进行操作后，通过页面元素的变化，清晰的展现当前状态变化</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"3-层级\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%E5%B1%82%E7%BA%A7\" aria-label=\"3 层级 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 层级</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>层级关系明确</strong>：控制面板展开后，展示内容与标题应有明确的层级区分，可在字体、背景等方面做结构化区分 <a href=\"http://10.179.234.214:8000/component/Collapse/#%E4%BF%9D%E8%AF%81%E5%B1%82%E7%BA%A7%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE\">常见问题>></a></li>\n<li><strong>嵌套限制</strong>：为保证层级清晰，结构明了，建议折叠面板不进行过多层级嵌套，最多嵌套一次折叠面板 <a href=\"http://10.179.234.214:8000/component/Collapse/#%E5%B5%8C%E5%A5%97%E5%B1%82%E7%BA%A7%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%9A\">常见问题>></a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"行为\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA\" aria-label=\"行为 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>行为</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>触发区为标题与折叠icon的整个背景区域，折叠前后折叠icon需要同步改变</li>\n<li>当内容展开时，折叠icon箭头向上；当内容收起时，折叠icon箭头向下</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"常规折叠面板\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%84%E6%8A%98%E5%8F%A0%E9%9D%A2%E6%9D%BF\" aria-label=\"常规折叠面板 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>常规折叠面板</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>折叠面板默认为全部收起或默认首项展开（推荐）</li>\n<li>点击一个触发区展开其层级下的折叠内容。若再次点击另一个触发区，展开该层级下的折叠内容，上一个折叠内容不收起。若折叠内容在容器中无法完全展示，可通过上下左右滑动查看全部内容</li>\n<li>点击已被展开的触发区，折叠内容收起</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"手风琴-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%89%8B%E9%A3%8E%E7%90%B4-1\" aria-label=\"手风琴 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>手风琴</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>折叠面板默认为全部收起或默认首项展开（推荐）</li>\n<li>点击一个触发区展开其层级下的折叠内容。若再次点击另一个触发区，展开该层级下的折叠内容，同时上一个折叠内容收起。若折叠内容在容器中无法完全展示，可通过上下左右滑动查看全部内容。</li>\n<li>点击已被展开的触发区，折叠内容收起</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"常见问题\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\" aria-label=\"常见问题 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>常见问题</h2>\n<h3 id=\"保证层级结构明确\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BF%9D%E8%AF%81%E5%B1%82%E7%BA%A7%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE\" aria-label=\"保证层级结构明确 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>保证层级结构明确</h3>\n<p>涉及比较复杂的层级结构，需在样式上做区分，保证结构明确易读</p>\n<div class=\"u-md-flex-without-bg\">\n   <div class=\"u-md-mr24\">\n      <p><i class=\"u-md-suggested\"></i>层级样式明确</p>\n      <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1113px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 45.27777777777778%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image alt\" title=\"desc\" src=\"/u-design/static/6e246629b8a708d53bd8295df21cd894/430fb/%E5%B1%82%E7%BA%A7%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0.png\" srcset=\"/u-design/static/6e246629b8a708d53bd8295df21cd894/8ef26/%E5%B1%82%E7%BA%A7%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/6e246629b8a708d53bd8295df21cd894/c4481/%E5%B1%82%E7%BA%A7%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/6e246629b8a708d53bd8295df21cd894/430fb/%E5%B1%82%E7%BA%A7%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0.png 1113w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1113px) 100vw, 1113px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">desc</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n      <p><i class=\"u-md-not-suggested\"></i>结构不清晰层级不明确</p>\n      <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1035px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 19.72222222222222%; position: relative; bottom: 0; le